fields.name: Profile Picture Description
fields.value: My sitting at the rock wall ruins of Hawes Station, an Overland Stage/Pony Express/ Emigrant Trail stop, The ruins sit on the slope of a sage & rock covered hill. I am wearing a black mask, white overshirt, grey t-shirt, blue jeans, and grey hiking boots.

fields.name: Header Picture Description
fields.value: A mature bald eagle takes off from a wooden fence post. Black wings wide, white tail flared, white head focused intently on the prey in the snow covered field. A snowy blue mountainside fills the background.
